    "title": "Career Opportunity Medical Officer at Aurobindo Pharma",
    "description": "Aurobindo Pharma has an exciting opening for a Medical Officer at our Mumbai office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Aurobindo Pharma:\nAurobindo Pharma is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ICU Management\n• Proficiency in Medical Ethics\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Aurobindo Pharma!",
